    question:'Is there guilt tangled up with a grief you\'re carrying about missing a loved one\'s final moments — and could you name that guilt honestly to God this week?',
    prayer:'Lord, comfort me in the grief I couldn\'t fully mourn in person. Untangle any guilt from the sorrow, and hold me in both. Amen.',
