    takeaways:['Spiritual dryness can be a long season, not just a bad week','Renewal doesn\'t always look dramatic — sometimes it\'s just walking without fainting','Hope, sustained slowly, is still the hope this promise honors'],
    question:'In your current long season, what would \'walking without fainting\' realistically look like this week?',
